{"tid":2100616,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國武術協會：不得自創門派及自封大師","createTime":"2020-07-09T07:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T11:54:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"57944b2d399268fd9dc6e9dcae53d1600aa1847e","tid":2100616,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"中國武術協會發出《關於加強行業自律弘揚武術文化的倡議書》，要求習武之人「提升武德修養，遵守職業道德」，不得隨意自創拳種及門派，強調武術之人要根據《中國武術段位制》去評價武術水平，不得自封「大師」、「掌門」、「嫡傳」等稱號。<br />\n<br />\n《倡議書》提到，支持習武者參加武術競技比賽和交流，但不得參加「不分項目、性別、年齡、體重級別」等不規範賽事，並嚴禁習武者以「拜師收徒」、「賀壽慶典」等名義，炒作斂財。 68歲自稱「混元形意太極掌門人」的馬保國，5月中曾經與業餘選手在擂台對賽，結果不足30秒就被對手3度擊倒，昏迷送院，引起討論。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346223&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmqRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=3d2f4ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346223</a>"},{"pid":"5877e62f4493ab320c6a37cd995ae73f3d5f17f4","tid":2100616,"uid":9413,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dte73B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dte73B.jpg&h=21a8a43e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223c04bd80c2bf92700d5e2ca5deeb5fe103bd19","tid":2100616,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e771ff068c4dc8544775097bd105943336883283","tid":2100616,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"五嶽劍派？"},{"pid":"a6bddbd4fc4691b133fa69007e8d36eee98c1d2e","tid":2100616,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5877e62f4493ab320c6a37cd995ae73f3d5f17f4","tid":2100616,"uid":9413,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dte73B.jpg